Triceradon finally reached the Cybertronian Fire. A dozen or so Maximals were 
outside defending the heavily damaged CF against an army of Alliance bots. 
Triceradon transformed to robot mode and took out his launcher. He stood to 
to the side of the battle where he began to pick out his target.
